1
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:34,920
What Bro Min and I are gonna do

2
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,320
is offline sales.

3
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,800
Don't doubt it, folks.

4
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:40,680
Once offline sales spread nationwide,

5
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,280
a lot of online traffic

6
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:44,400
will convert into offline customers.

7
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,080
But this investment,

8
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,360
isn't it a bit too much?

9
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:49,320
Small family businesses like ours

10
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:50,720
don't have that kind of money.

11
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,840
Of course, getting rich comes with risks.

12
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,720
Let's do this.

13
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,320
Those who want to hop on board,

14
00:01:57,640 --> 00:02:00,640
sign up and register with Bro Min.

15
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,880
If you're not willing,

16
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:04,280
if you don't want to take the risk,

17
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,120
that's fine too.

18
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,160
We won't force anyone.

19
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:07,840
Purely voluntary, purely voluntary.

20
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:08,800
Right.

21
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:09,919
Wanna get rich?

22
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:11,760
Come on, come on.

23
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,160
Let me walk you through this.

24
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:13,640
Uh, Bro Min,

25
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,560
you guys chat first.

26
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,520
You go ahead and talk.

27
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,320
You've gotta explain it,

28
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:17,840
walk us through this in detail.

29
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,520
In today's market environment,

30
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,200
we can't go it alone anymore.

31
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,720
Why set up a cooperative?

32
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,880
So we can all pull together as one.

33
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:27,480
We're all brothers here.

34
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,400
Let me speak from the heart.

35
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,520
Before, no matter what happened,

36
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,800
I caused more trouble than anyone.

37
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:35,560
Now I've completely seen the light.

38
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,840
Bro Min, no question, he's loyal.

39
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:38,720
He's top-notch.

40
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:39,440
That's right, that's right.

41
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:41,360
Xuan Yan and Lin Yiran

42
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,800
are way better than any of us here.

43
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,840
They genuinely mean well for us,

44
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,400
bringing us along to make some money.

45
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:49,600
Investing is really investing in people.

46
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:50,360
Am I right?

47
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:53,440
I'm hopping on this co-op boat.

48
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:55,360
I'm putting in a few hundred grand.

49
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:57,280
As for your little bits of change,

50
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,280
stop hesitating.

51
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,640
Just get on board and do it.

52
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:01,400
Erhu, where'd you get hundreds of grand?

53
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,040
Yeah, right?

54
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,080
Never mind where I got it.

55
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,280
I'll borrow money to invest.

56
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,400
From now on, quit calling me Erhu.

57
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:08,600
Call me Boss Hu.

58
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,600
Boss Hu, Boss Hu, Boss Hu.

59
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,000
Boss Hu, Boss Hu, Boss Hu.

60
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,560
Boss Hu.

61
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,560
Erhu's right.

62
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,880
My little patch of land,

63
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:20,200
I can't just cling to it anymore.

64
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,840
Big factories will soon squeeze us out.

65
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,440
I'm in.

66
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,280
Great, great.

67
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,040
If everyone wants to do this,

68
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,560
nobody can sit idle.

69
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:28,800
Each family must play to their strengths.

70
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:29,680
Then here's the deal.

71
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,600
Our machines are good.

72
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:33,800
I'll handle cutting and pressing.

73
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,400
I'll take care of packaging.

74
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,680
Then I'll handle sourcing raw materials.

75
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,600
Each family plays to their strengths,

76
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,520
avoiding infighting.

77
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,080
Right.

78
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:41,720
That's exactly right.

79
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,920
We're doing this, sure,

80
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,920
but no faking or cutting corners,

81
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:46,960
no deliberate price undercutting.

82
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:49,520
Okay, okay, sure.

83
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,640
We'll unify our standards,

84
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:52,920
unify our pricing.

85
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,080
We stick together,

86
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,520
and grab our share nationwide.

87
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,120
Sound good?

88
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,800
Let's do it, do it, do it!

89
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:00,320
Great!

90
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:01,360
Come on.

91
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:11,600
Great, great, great.

92
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,360
I hereby declare

93
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:18,040
the Taohua Town Xuan Paper Cultural Creative Cooperative

94
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,680
officially established!

95
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,680
Great, great, great!

96
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:13,920
Sister Xu

97
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:16,080
This is salted duck I cured at home.

98
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:16,880
It's nothing fancy.

99
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,400
Take it home and steam it for Xuan Yan.

100
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,800
I can't accept it, I can't.

101
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,600
You have to take it.

102
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,400
No, no, no.

103
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,400
Sister Xu is here.

104
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,480
Sister Xu is here.

105
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:24,360
I really can't accept it.

106
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,080
Sister Xu.

107
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:27,120
My daughter bought this cosmetic in Shanghai.

108
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,080
She asked me to give it to you.

109
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,040
She specifically told me.

110
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,040
We're getting older.

111
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,200
We really need to take care of our skin.

112
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:32,520
I can't accept it.

113
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:33,920
My husband Xuan said,

114
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,680
we can't take things from everyone.

115
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,680
What do you mean you can't take it?

116
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,600
I raised this chicken myself with grain.

117
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,800
It's nothing valuable.

118
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,520
Still, I can't accept it.

119
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,240
If you keep this up,

120
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,960
I won't dare walk down this street anymore.

121
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,920
Sister Xiumei, just take it.

122
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,480
Your Xuan Yan is so capable.

123
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,360
He earns his own money,

124
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:48,240
and he doesn't forget

125
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,880
to help us older folks make money too.

126
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:52,120
We can't thank him enough.

127
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:54,000
Isn't that just what he should do?

128
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,920
Sister Xu.

129
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:57,120
We watched Xuan Yan grow up.

130
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:59,360
As a kid, he used to play with my Xiaowei.

131
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:00,760
He ate at my place every day.

132
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,000
Every day he'd crane his neck,

133
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,480
staring at the cured ham under our eaves.

134
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,120
Every time he came over,

135
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:08,120
I'd stew him a little bowl of it.

136
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,080
You see?

137
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:10,360
All you aunties, ever since he was small,

138
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,560
watched him grow up and took care of him.

139
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,360
He should thank you all, right?

140
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,000
Take it.

141
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,200
This, this, this...

142
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:18,240
No, I can't, I can't.

143
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,160
Well, we'll be heading back.

144
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:20,680
Take care now.

145
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,880
What's up? Why'd you call me here

146
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,120
in such a hurry?

147
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,000
You're here.

148
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:40,560
Wait, you only ordered coffee for yourself?

149
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,440
Where's mine?

150
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:42,800
I called you here

151
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,840
because I have something serious to discuss.

152
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,640
Just say it straight.

153
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:56,680
Let me ask you,

154
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,440
have you been happy lately?

155
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,240
I guess so.

156
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,680
"I guess so"?

157
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,520
Happy is happy.

158
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:06,920
Not happy is not happy.

159
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:11,080
Then... let's say happy.

160
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,240
Why?

161
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,600
Why?

162
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:21,280
Well, work's been going smoothly lately.

163
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,320
Some of the projects

164
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:24,880
are starting to take shape.

165
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,320
That's it?

166
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,240
That's it.

167
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,920
So your happiness doesn't include me?

168
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,200
Shouldn't it be

169
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:36,280
because we share a common dream,

170
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:38,040
fight side by side,

171
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,280
and make it happen together

172
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,640
that you feel happy?

173
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,600
So oblivious.

174
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,240
Yes.

175
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,320
But I think

176
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:46,840
you should have more joy and happiness.

177
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,120
Much more.

178
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,120
Ready to come back with me yet?

179
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:04,480
Let's sit down another day

180
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,480
to talk about this,

181
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,200
okay?

182
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:08,440
I have a meeting soon.

183
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,360
Fine, hold on.

184
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,560
What's this?

185
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,320
Open it and see.

186
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,679
Mugwort cakes my mom made for you herself.

187
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:43,440
Thank auntie for me, please.

188
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:47,280
All right, hurry up and eat.

189
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,800
They'll get cold soon.

190
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:11,920
Fished for hours

191
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,680
and didn't catch a single fish.

192
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:16,040
Old Zhang kept making excuses.

193
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:19,120
Said it's a wild pond with few fish.

194
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,000
I figured,

195
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,680
he was testing my fishing skills.

196
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:24,400
I was about to show him what I've got.

197
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:25,880
And then, guess what happened?

198
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,000
A local came by and said

199
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,240
that this pond

200
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,840
was just filled with water this morning.

201
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,400
Last night it was still dry.

202
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:36,120
That really tests your skills!

203
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,000
Chairman,

204
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,720
I scouted this pond today.

205
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,080
I guarantee you'll be satisfied.

206
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,800
Enough, stop making excuses. Let's go.

207
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:43,720
Come on, let's go.

208
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:44,440
Watch your step.

209
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,080
Get moving.

210
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,760
Goodbye, Chairman.

211
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,280
Sister Xin,

212
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:59,240
these past two days the Chairman's been here,

213
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,680
he hasn't mentioned Xuan Yan or the co-op.

214
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,760
As if none of it ever happened.

215
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:06,640
Could it be he's had a change of heart

216
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:08,120
and tolerated Xuan Yan's provocation?

217
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,200
Stop dreaming.

218
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,880
This is just the calm before the storm.

219
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,360
Back when I was at the group,

220
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,040
serving as the Chairman's assistant,

221
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,880
I discovered a vice president

222
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,800
was colluding with a supplier,

223
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:22,840
using his position for personal gain.

224
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,080
One time,

225
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,600
I caught him with hard evidence.

226
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,160
And I

227
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:28,280
reported the matter to the Chairman.

228
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,480
By protocol,

229
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,280
we should've gone straight to the police.

230
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:33,560
But the Chairman,

231
00:10:33,760 --> 00:10:35,080
not only wouldn't let me call the police,

232
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:37,240
he also warned me not to tip him off.

233
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,080
He told me to keep gathering evidence.

234
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,800
Later, this vice president

235
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,560
got greedier and greedier,

236
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,840
and I gathered more and more evidence.

237
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,040
Right at that moment,

238
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:50,000
the Chairman had me step out and expose him.

239
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:52,200
In the end, this vice president,

240
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,840
because the amount involved was huge,

241
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,760
was convicted of embezzlement

242
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,600
and sentenced to three years in prison.

243
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,440
You mean the Chairman's brother-in-law?

244
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:04,120
So I couldn't stay at the group anymore.

245
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:06,560
The Chairman sent me to Taohua Town.

246
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:07,480
Of course,

247
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,520
that was the outcome I wanted most.

248
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:12,040
Now I understand

249
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,840
why you're so worried about Xuan Yan.

250
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:16,280
If he's that ruthless with his own in-law,

251
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:18,360
there's no way he'll let Xuan Yan off.

252
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:21,000
Now I suspect

253
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:24,160
the Chairman is waiting until every

254
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:26,760
Taohua Xuan paper business takes the bait.

255
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:27,840
Then he'll pull the net shut.

256
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,120
So the bigger the co-op grows,

257
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:33,120
the more they invest,

258
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,280
the worse it gets for Xuan Yan.

259
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,520
If it's really as I suspect,

260
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:43,480
Taohua Town will be doomed forever.

261
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,880
Put like that, it all adds up.

262
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,840
The Chairman isn't fishing at all.

263
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:55,120
We can't let this go on.

264
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,880
He's already used me once.

265
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:01,240
I won't be the one to doom Taohua Town.

266
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:25,000
Miss, has the person you're waiting for not arrived yet?

267
00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:27,080
Would you like a coffee refill?

268
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,440
No, thank you.

269
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:45,880
Over here.

270
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,160
Chairman.

271
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:50,720
Sorry to disturb your rest.

272
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:52,920
No, I don't sleep this early.

273
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:53,880
I'm watching the game.

274
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:56,240
The second half is about to start.

275
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,880
What is it? Make it quick.

276
00:12:58,160 --> 00:13:00,600
It's about Xuan Yan opening physical stores.

277
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,160
Chairman.

278
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:05,720
I've gone over Xuan Yan's plan

279
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,320
one more time.

280
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:09,520
I think it's highly feasible.

281
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:10,880
From the group's perspective,

282
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:12,320
I've really thought this through.

283
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,520
I believe that for both sides,

284
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:15,440
only through good cooperation

285
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:17,640
can we achieve the best outcome.

286
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,640
This is the feasibility report

287
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:20,760
from my market research.

288
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:21,600
Please take a look.

289
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,640
Xuan Yan is right.

290
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,960
This is the future direction

291
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,120
of our cultural creative business.

292
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:30,680
Daya Zhai has already positioned itself.

293
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:32,720
We can't miss this opportunity.

294
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:35,960
Ms. Xin,

295
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,240
this matter,

296
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:40,000
stop thinking about it from now on.

297
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:44,480
Chairman, please let me finish.

298
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,160
Ms. Xin.

299
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:46,920
I'm truly sorry.

300
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:49,400
I really don't want to discuss this anymore.

301
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,000
Sorry.

302
00:14:01,760 --> 00:14:02,480
Ms. Xin,

303
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:04,880
there's something I'd rather not say.

304
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:08,840
Do you know what your problem is?

305
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:12,080
You always ponder things you shouldn't.

306
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:14,040
And what you should be thinking about,

307
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:15,440
you never quite get right.

308
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:20,240
I believe my concerns are very necessary.

309
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:21,520
Because I know

310
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,240
what you're thinking.

311
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:31,080
What am I thinking?

312
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:32,280
Alright.

313
00:14:33,160 --> 00:14:35,480
Tell me. Let's see if you've grown.

314
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,840
If I'm not mistaken,

315
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:39,720
right now, you're fishing.

316
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:40,840
And in fact,

317
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,640
your fish has already bitten.

318
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:43,960
You're just playing it along.

319
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,360
Tiring it out until it gives up.

320
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:46,520
Then you tame it.

321
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,360
If Xuan Yan behaves,

322
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:51,760
you let him quietly

323
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,360
keep making money for Daya Zhai.

324
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,600
If he doesn't cooperate,

325
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:55,880
we crush him.

326
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:57,000
End it once and for all.

327
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,760
Then Xuan Bao'er designs still belong to you.

328
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:01,600
No one can touch your piece of the pie.

329
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:02,880
Am I right?

330
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:07,760
Ms. Xin,

331
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,320
I was right.

332
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:14,480
You always ponder things you shouldn't.

333
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:16,040
You're always saying

334
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:17,640
I lack the bigger picture.

335
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:19,440
But let me tell you,

336
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:21,600
today I'm thinking from the group's height,

337
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:22,400
that's my perspective.

338
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:26,880
Go on, tell me.

339
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:31,240
Chairman, you're a master angler.

340
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:33,880
But I know Xuan Yan very well too.

341
00:15:33,880 --> 00:15:36,480
I believe if you keep fishing this way,

342
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,920
not only will you lose the big fish,

343
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:41,240
the rod will snap, and both will perish.

344
00:15:42,280 --> 00:15:43,840
You and Xuan Yan are different.

345
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:46,120
You're mature and steady,

346
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:48,440
and you consider everything thoroughly.

347
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,680
But Xuan Yan,

348
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:51,000
he's young and hot-headed.

349
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:52,720
He acts without thinking of consequences.

350
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:54,600
Once things turn sour between us,

351
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:57,040
we'll never have a chance to cooperate again.

352
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:58,240
Our cultural creative products

353
00:15:58,240 --> 00:16:00,840
target young consumers.

354
00:16:00,880 --> 00:16:03,600
We need to keep igniting the market

355
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:05,160
and constantly update and iterate.

356
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:06,520
Once our products

357
00:16:06,520 --> 00:16:07,880
don't have follow-ups,

358
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:09,960
we'll quickly lose market momentum.

359
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,120
I made this.

360
00:16:16,160 --> 00:16:18,600
Our Jinling Twelve Beauties and Tang Ladies

361
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:20,240
have steadily declining sales figures.

362
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:21,240
Then you'll understand

363
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:23,360
I'm not just crying wolf here.

364
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:27,320
Chairman,

365
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:31,520
we could hire another designer,

366
00:16:31,760 --> 00:16:32,880
but the high cost aside,

367
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:34,520
let's set that concern aside for now.

368
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,920
Would his new design concepts

369
00:16:36,920 --> 00:16:38,840
really be accepted

370
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:39,920
by today's consumers?

371
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,360
Xuan Yan is different.

372
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:44,240
We've already put his work on the market,

373
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,720
and it's been tested by the market.

374
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:49,240
Yes,

375
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:51,240
we can both deny

376
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:52,880
the way he handles himself,

377
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:55,080
but neither of us can deny his talent.

378
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:55,880
Isn't that right?

379
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,640
If you cripple him,

380
00:16:58,320 --> 00:17:00,240
in the end, we'll be crippling ourselves.

381
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:02,000
By then, both sides will end up

382
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,400
in a lose-lose situation.

383
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:18,400
What's your idea? Go ahead.

384
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:21,240
Chairman,

385
00:17:21,520 --> 00:17:22,680
I'm begging you,

386
00:17:22,839 --> 00:17:24,280
give him one more chance.

387
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:25,640
I'll go talk to him first.

388
00:17:26,119 --> 00:17:26,960
I believe

389
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:27,839
our Daya Zhai

390
00:17:27,839 --> 00:17:29,760
can take another form of partnership

391
00:17:29,760 --> 00:17:31,520
to participate in the offline cooperative.

392
00:17:31,520 --> 00:17:33,120
As long as you accept this plan,

393
00:17:33,360 --> 00:17:34,760
I'll bring him over

394
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:36,000
to meet with you in person.

395
00:17:36,040 --> 00:17:37,120
What do you say?

396
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,240
Fine.

397
00:17:46,520 --> 00:17:48,520
But I don't have much time to give you.

398
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:50,760
Tomorrow, I'm heading back to Shenzhen.

399
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:52,400
What time's your flight?

400
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:53,400
Two-thirty.

401
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,640
I promise, within that time,

402
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:57,240
I'll bring him to meet with you.

403
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:18,000
Ms. Xin.

404
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:25,000
Why aren't you answering my calls, Xuan Yan?

405
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:27,320
I knew what you were going to say.

406
00:18:27,320 --> 00:18:28,240
So I didn't pick up.

407
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:32,400
The chairman is willing to talk again.

408
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:35,320
Too late. Production's already started.

409
00:18:35,320 --> 00:18:37,520
Everything's already up and running.

410
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:38,480
See?

411
00:18:38,600 --> 00:18:40,280
Just got back from the factory. All's well.

412
00:18:41,080 --> 00:18:41,720
Ms. Xin.

413
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:43,440
It doesn't matter that you've started production.

414
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:45,440
Daya Zhai can still invest more.

415
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:47,000
You could expand production.

416
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:48,680
It'd be a win-win situation.

417
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:49,800
Wouldn't that be great?

418
00:18:49,840 --> 00:18:52,400
I've already done all I could last time.

419
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:54,280
And what did I get in return?

420
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:55,520
Nothing but humiliation.

421
00:18:55,600 --> 00:18:57,520
I don't see any point in talking to him again.

422
00:18:57,720 --> 00:18:59,720
Cooperation's always better than confrontation.

423
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,520
I just don't get it.

424
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:04,680
Why do you keep pushing me

425
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:06,600
to work under his thumb?

426
00:19:07,120 --> 00:19:07,720
Xuan Yan.

427
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:09,160
I'll say it again.

428
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:11,160
Deal or no deal,

429
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:12,960
you're still our friend.

430
00:19:14,040 --> 00:19:15,160
If you'd like,

431
00:19:15,560 --> 00:19:17,000
stay and have a working lunch with us.

432
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:21,920
Yes, yes, stay for the working lunch.

433
00:19:21,920 --> 00:19:22,640
I'll go order a few dishes.

434
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,800
No thanks. I've got things to do.

435
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:27,680
Ms. Xin, at least eat before you go.

436
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:30,520
Ms. Xin.

437
00:19:31,320 --> 00:19:32,120
Ms. Xin!

438
00:19:40,600 --> 00:19:42,160
The municipal committee secretariat reminded us

439
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:43,520
Deputy Mayor Qin requested

440
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:46,240
No fanfare, no lengthy speeches

441
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:48,760
Don't disrupt the company's normal operations

442
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:50,800
Right

443
00:19:50,840 --> 00:19:52,280
We must not disrupt

444
00:19:52,280 --> 00:19:53,720
the company's normal work

445
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:55,240
Just a few of us will accompany him

446
00:19:55,560 --> 00:19:56,080
Lin Yiran

447
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:58,480
Today you'll be the main one reporting to the leader

448
00:19:58,920 --> 00:20:00,480
Keep it simple and brief

449
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:05,840
Go

450
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:09,240
Did everyone hear what I just said?

451
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:09,600
Hello, Sister Xin

452
00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:11,120
So everyone, make sure the preparations

453
00:20:11,120 --> 00:20:12,120
I'm in the middle of something here

454
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:12,800
are done thoroughly

455
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:13,360
Alright

456
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:20,360
Yiran

457
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:23,000
Wait, Sister Xin, what's going on?

458
00:20:23,040 --> 00:20:24,120
Did you just say

459
00:20:24,120 --> 00:20:25,880
all of Xuan Yan's cultural design patents

460
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:27,400
now belong to Daya Zhai? Is that right?

461
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:30,040
When I found out the chairman did this, I...

462
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:32,760
I didn't tell Xuan Yan in time

463
00:20:32,760 --> 00:20:34,480
Wait, how is what you did any different

464
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:35,720
from being robbers?

465
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:37,600
If I had told him back then,

466
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:40,120
our cooperation couldn't have continued

467
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:43,040
Xuan Yan would've lost a great opportunity

468
00:20:43,120 --> 00:20:45,040
and the cultural line wouldn't take off

469
00:20:45,040 --> 00:20:46,240
For both of us,

470
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:47,960
that wouldn't benefit anyone, right?

471
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:50,120
The chairman right now,

472
00:20:50,120 --> 00:20:53,160
it's just his self-protection strategy

473
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,760
Of course, I'm at fault too

474
00:20:55,760 --> 00:20:57,720
I kept holding on to the hope

475
00:20:57,720 --> 00:20:59,400
that as long as this cooperation

476
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:01,240
went ahead normally,

477
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:03,160
I could find a chance later

478
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,440
to make it up to him

479
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:05,840
I just never imagined

480
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:08,520
that because of the co-op issue,

481
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,320
it would end up like this

482
00:21:14,560 --> 00:21:16,040
Will you admit one more thing?

483
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:18,400
That you factored in your own future

484
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:19,560
as well

485
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:20,720
Right?

486
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,960
Yes, I did consider that

487
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:26,240
Unbelievable

488
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:27,000
Yiran

489
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:32,240
I admit to all my mistakes

490
00:21:32,320 --> 00:21:34,200
Can you hold me accountable later?

491
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:36,960
Can you help us right now?

492
00:21:37,520 --> 00:21:38,640
So what you mean is,

493
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:40,440
you tell me but not Xuan Yan,

494
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,960
because you want me to persuade him

495
00:21:41,960 --> 00:21:43,840
to cooperate with your chairman, right?

496
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,520
Xuan Yan can't know about this

497
00:21:46,040 --> 00:21:47,840
Once Xuan Yan finds out,

498
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:50,120
if we still use the patent issue

499
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:52,920
to force him to cooperate with the chairman,

500
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:54,840
the whole thing will fall apart

501
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:56,480
Yiran, I'm begging you

502
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:57,760
For Xuan Yan's sake,

503
00:21:57,880 --> 00:22:00,200
for the future of Taohua Town's industry,

504
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:01,560
please go talk to him

505
00:22:01,880 --> 00:22:02,560
Enough, enough, stop it

506
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:04,040
If he'll just talk to the chairman once

507
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:05,320
Listen to me, just stop talking

508
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:07,560
Deputy Mayor Qin is arriving at the co-op soon

509
00:22:07,560 --> 00:22:08,200
He'll be here any minute

510
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:09,160
I have to go, okay?

511
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:10,760
Yiran

512
00:22:11,600 --> 00:22:12,440
Yiran

513
00:22:12,560 --> 00:22:13,600
Yiran, listen to me

514
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:17,720
This is the only way to salvage the situation

515
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:20,200
Help Xuan Yan, and help me too, okay?

516
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:27,320
Yiran

517
00:22:29,280 --> 00:22:31,120
Yiran, I'll wait for your word, Yiran

518
00:22:49,560 --> 00:22:50,960
As you all can see, everyone,

519
00:22:50,960 --> 00:22:52,240
the place we've arrived at now

520
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:54,600
is part of Taohua Town's intangible heritage industry.

521
00:22:54,600 --> 00:22:56,800
Each piece bears its own auspicious meaning.

522
00:22:56,800 --> 00:22:58,400
With the holiday coming up soon,

523
00:22:58,400 --> 00:22:59,760
everyone can buy a lucky omen,

524
00:22:59,760 --> 00:23:00,680
a piece with good meaning.

525
00:23:00,920 --> 00:23:02,360
Now, everyone, take a look here.

526
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:04,680
Perfect conjugal bliss, blessings, and health.

527
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,840
Comrades, great work today.

528
00:23:48,840 --> 00:23:49,680
Hurry up.

529
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:51,040
The cafeteria's already serving.

530
00:23:51,040 --> 00:23:52,840
Pack up and go grab a meal.

531
00:23:52,840 --> 00:23:53,520
Alright.

532
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:54,960
Thanks for your hard work.

533
00:23:59,080 --> 00:23:59,880
Xiao Lin.

534
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:02,080
Xiao Lin.

535
00:24:02,800 --> 00:24:05,200
What's up? You seem off today.

536
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:07,720
Did I say something wrong again?

537
00:24:08,080 --> 00:24:09,000
No, not really.

538
00:24:09,040 --> 00:24:10,440
It's just that before we left,

539
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:12,200
you took a call in a panic.

540
00:24:12,280 --> 00:24:13,800
Who was it? Everything okay?

541
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:16,680
It's fine. I can handle it.

542
00:24:17,720 --> 00:24:18,520
Good then.

543
00:24:21,840 --> 00:24:24,160
You don't look so well, though.

544
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:25,280
Are you feeling sick?

545
00:24:25,600 --> 00:24:26,320
No.

546
00:24:26,320 --> 00:24:28,280
Don't worry, Secretary Peng. I'm fine.

547
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:32,000
So why didn't Xuan Yan show up today?

548
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,600
He promised he'd come.

549
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:35,880
But he still didn't show.

550
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,560
Oh, by the way, Yiran.

551
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:42,600
Daya Zhai is a key enterprise

552
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:44,400
we brought into Taohua Town.

553
00:24:44,760 --> 00:24:46,880
We can't let the co-op we're setting up

554
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:48,280
step on their interests.

555
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:50,320
It's about win-win cooperation.

556
00:24:50,520 --> 00:24:52,880
Keep that principle firmly in mind.

557
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:55,400
Understood.

558
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:57,000
Alright, let's eat.

559
00:25:05,600 --> 00:25:06,560
This won't do.

560
00:25:08,320 --> 00:25:10,760
The texture pattern is too shallow.

561
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,040
And the color's off, too.

562
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:12,440
Mom.

563
00:25:13,840 --> 00:25:14,680
Take a look.

564
00:25:15,120 --> 00:25:16,040
Is this the one?

565
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:19,960
Yes, yes, that's it.

566
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:25,760
Enough, enough.

567
00:25:26,560 --> 00:25:28,680
You've botched it a hundred times.

568
00:25:28,680 --> 00:25:30,040
Your son's right here.

569
00:25:30,040 --> 00:25:30,760
Why not ask him?

570
00:25:30,760 --> 00:25:32,120
Let him give you some advice.

571
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:33,560
Come on, tell your dad.

572
00:25:35,240 --> 00:25:38,120
You're imitating Mingren Hall paper, right?

573
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:42,600
See?

574
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,920
Should've asked Xuan Yan sooner.

575
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:48,000
This Mingren Hall paper,

576
00:25:48,120 --> 00:25:51,160
represented the peak of Yuan Dynasty papermaking.

577
00:25:51,520 --> 00:25:52,840
Originally made from mulberry bark.

578
00:25:53,080 --> 00:25:54,240
Sandalwood bark works, too.

579
00:25:54,840 --> 00:25:56,880
But this is a processed paper.

580
00:25:58,760 --> 00:26:00,040
A processed paper.

581
00:26:01,320 --> 00:26:02,120
Look here.

582
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:04,360
These patterns on the surface,

583
00:26:04,760 --> 00:26:06,120
they aren't formed during scooping.

584
00:26:06,120 --> 00:26:07,720
After the paper is scooped out,

585
00:26:07,800 --> 00:26:09,120
it goes through post-processing.

586
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,800
Waxing,

587
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:11,800
burnishing,

588
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:14,000
several steps before it's finished.

589
00:26:14,520 --> 00:26:17,240
The Xuan family excels at making Xuan paper.

590
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:18,520
But when it comes to processed paper,

591
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:21,280
the Suzhou craftsmen have always been best.

592
00:26:22,320 --> 00:26:23,640
Don't bother. It's hopeless.

593
00:26:24,560 --> 00:26:26,520
See, if that's the case,

594
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:28,440
we got it wrong from the start.

595
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:30,520
No wonder you couldn't scoop it right.

596
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:32,240
I told you all a long time ago.

597
00:26:32,240 --> 00:26:34,840
Don't rush the scooping.

598
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:36,160
Find a sample paper first.

599
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:37,320
But you wouldn't listen.

600
00:26:37,560 --> 00:26:38,800
In our household,

601
00:26:40,280 --> 00:26:42,240
we don't have this kind of sample.

602
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:44,440
This kind of paper,

603
00:26:44,520 --> 00:26:47,320
I only heard of it from Grandpa as a kid.

604
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:48,680
Never saw it myself.

605
00:26:49,240 --> 00:26:52,800
Supposedly, during the Qianlong era,

606
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:55,840
this craft was already lost.

607
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:02,440
We're just trying every possible way

608
00:27:02,520 --> 00:27:03,720
to recreate it.

609
00:27:04,120 --> 00:27:07,520
To fill in a gap left by the ancestors.

610
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:14,440
Dad.

611
00:27:15,720 --> 00:27:16,800
Don't rush it.

612
00:27:17,120 --> 00:27:18,480
Once I finish up these next few days,

613
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:19,920
I'll study it with you.

614
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:25,000
If needed, we'll visit the Palace Museum.

615
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,960
If that fails, I'll take you to Suzhou.

616
00:27:26,960 --> 00:27:29,120
We'll study the crafting technique together.

617
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:30,320
I refuse to believe

618
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:32,480
we can't recreate this Mingren Hall paper.

619
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:33,520
We'll figure it out, right?

620
00:27:33,520 --> 00:27:35,040
Right, I'll buy the tickets.

621
00:27:35,520 --> 00:27:36,280
Forget it.

622
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:39,680
I'm just tinkering to pass the time.

623
00:27:42,360 --> 00:27:44,480
If we actually managed to make it,

624
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:48,800
it wouldn't even be that interesting.

625
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:03,720
Make a fine paper worthy of our ancestors.

626
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:06,920
Who came up with this lousy idea?

627
00:28:07,200 --> 00:28:10,280
Not me. He thought of it himself.

628
00:28:11,800 --> 00:28:13,000
It's a nice idea.

629
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:14,520
But he hasn't got the skill.

630
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:16,600
Just stewing in frustration.

631
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:17,320
Hello?

632
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:20,560
You're already at the courtyard?

633
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:21,600
Who is it?

634
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:23,120
Lin Yiran.

635
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:24,200
I'll go check.

636
00:28:24,200 --> 00:28:25,000
No, no, no.

637
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:26,680
I'm coming right out.

638
00:28:33,560 --> 00:28:35,600
Why didn't you tell me you were coming?

639
00:28:35,600 --> 00:28:36,400
My parents are here.

640
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:37,520
Come on, let's head home.

641
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:40,680
Wait, I need to talk to you.

642
00:28:40,800 --> 00:28:42,320
Can't we talk about it back home?

643
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:46,440
The chairwoman is at a hotel in town.

644
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:47,480
Xin Ran is there too.

645
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,920
She wants you to come talk.

646
00:28:49,400 --> 00:28:50,680
I already told Xin Ran everything.

647
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:51,480
What's going on?

648
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:55,440
Why are you getting mixed up in this?

649
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:58,040
I just think she has a point.

650
00:28:58,040 --> 00:28:59,760
Better to make peace than hold grudges.

651
00:28:59,840 --> 00:29:00,840
And I think

652
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:03,200
if Daya Zhai partners with the co-op,

653
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:04,680
Xuan Bao'er will have a better future.

654
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:07,160
And Sister Xin Ran won't be in such a bind.

655
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:08,960
This has nothing to do with her anymore.

656
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:11,120
But you're the head of the co-op.

657
00:29:11,680 --> 00:29:14,160
You should set aside grudges and think big-picture.

658
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:16,640
After all, it's good for the co-op.

659
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:17,680
You should go.

660
00:29:19,560 --> 00:29:20,520
Let's leave it at that.

661
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:22,000
Come on, let's go home.

662
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:24,640
Wait, Sister Xin Ran is waiting to hear back.

663
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:32,320
Please enjoy.

664
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:40,720
Chairwoman.

665
00:29:43,320 --> 00:29:44,120
Where is he?

666
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:48,880
He hasn't arrived yet.

667
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:53,480
Chairwoman, let's wait a little longer.

668
00:29:53,480 --> 00:29:54,640
There's still time.

669
00:29:54,760 --> 00:29:56,440
You won't miss your flight.

670
00:30:08,520 --> 00:30:09,640
I just feel

671
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:12,240
I shouldn't have to beg Zheng Guohui

672
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,520
to throw me a bone.

673
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:14,800
Right?

674
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:17,880
Is that why you came today?

675
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:19,480
No.

676
00:30:20,440 --> 00:30:21,600
I just thought...

677
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:25,040
Please, just go see him.

678
00:30:26,280 --> 00:30:27,600
What's wrong with you, Lin Yiran?

679
00:30:28,760 --> 00:30:30,280
Are you in some kind of trouble?

680
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:31,760
No.

681
00:30:31,760 --> 00:30:34,640
I just want you to talk to the chairman.

682
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:35,920
Please, just go.

683
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:36,720
Miss Lin.

684
00:30:37,560 --> 00:30:39,160
Mom, why are you out here?

685
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:40,040
Move aside.

686
00:30:40,400 --> 00:30:41,160
Miss Lin.

687
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:41,880
Auntie.

688
00:30:42,680 --> 00:30:45,080
Why haven't you visited us in so long?

689
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:46,480
Uncle.

690
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:50,680
I'm... I'm sorry, I...

691
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:53,640
Don't you dare apologize.

692
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:55,120
You've done right by everyone.

693
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:57,120
You've helped our family so much.

694
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:59,480
It's just that you haven't come around lately.

695
00:30:59,480 --> 00:31:00,760
Uncle Xuan and I

696
00:31:00,760 --> 00:31:02,640
have been missing you, talking about you.

697
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:09,960
Your mother, admittedly, was in the wrong.

698
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:12,840
And the consequences were quite serious.

699
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:15,240
But you don't need to avoid us.

700
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,120
What's going on here?

701
00:31:25,040 --> 00:31:26,240
What did you do to her?

702
00:31:26,440 --> 00:31:27,680
Nothing... nothing, Uncle.

703
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:28,840
Did you bully her?

704
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:29,040
No.

705
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:29,640
Did he bully you?

706
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:30,520
No, Auntie.

707
00:31:30,520 --> 00:31:30,880
I...

708
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:31,520
Well...

709
00:31:33,840 --> 00:31:35,760
Sister Xin Ran and I

710
00:31:35,760 --> 00:31:38,000
just don't want Xuan Yan to fall out with Daya Zhai.

711
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:40,480
We want him to go talk with the chairman

712
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:42,880
to try to secure a deal with the co-op, that's all.

713
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:46,520
Xuan Yan.

714
00:31:46,800 --> 00:31:48,480
Miss Lin's idea is a great one.

715
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:50,040
Go have a talk with that boss.

716
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:51,880
After all, a partnership is a good thing.

717
00:31:52,440 --> 00:31:54,040
You two don't understand.

718
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:56,760
That chairman of Daya Zhai, Zheng Guohui,

719
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:59,400
he's arrogant and has no respect for people.

720
00:31:59,520 --> 00:32:01,280
Let him be arrogant, whatever.

721
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:03,040
But disrespect is unacceptable.

722
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:05,040
If he won't cooperate, then forget it.

723
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:08,600
But now, he's given some ground.

724
00:32:08,760 --> 00:32:10,280
So don't be so stubborn.

725
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,280
Daya Zhai

726
00:32:11,280 --> 00:32:12,920
did give you a chance, after all.

727
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:15,320
You could even say he nurtured you.

728
00:32:15,760 --> 00:32:17,280
That's what you call the grace of recognition.

729
00:32:17,280 --> 00:32:19,640
Whatever he does, we won't worry about that.

730
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:21,120
But we have to understand

731
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:23,320
the value of repaying kindness.

732
00:32:23,800 --> 00:32:24,640
Exactly.

733
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:26,840
Son, your dad's right.

734
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:28,720
A person must have a conscience.

735
00:32:36,400 --> 00:32:37,320
What's the matter with you?

736
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:39,840
Why are you stomping your foot?

737
00:32:39,840 --> 00:32:40,320
No.

738
00:32:40,320 --> 00:32:41,120
I'll go.

739
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:42,960
I'll go.

740
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:50,560
Xin Ran.

741
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:52,760
I'm late, aren't I?

742
00:33:00,320 --> 00:33:01,680
Early or late, it makes no difference.

743
00:33:02,080 --> 00:33:02,920
What do you mean?

744
00:33:03,840 --> 00:33:06,800
The chairman said we can partner up,

745
00:33:06,920 --> 00:33:08,800
but you need to sign this contract.

746
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:12,280
An equity partnership agreement.

747
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:21,040
Wait, am I seeing this right?

748
00:33:22,320 --> 00:33:24,000
Daya Zhai doesn't want to spend a cent,

749
00:33:24,520 --> 00:33:25,520
yet wants to take

750
00:33:25,520 --> 00:33:26,880
fifty-one percent of the shares.

751
00:33:27,520 --> 00:33:29,760
Your chairman really has no shame!

752
00:33:29,840 --> 00:33:32,160
Who does Zheng Guohui think he is, being so overbearing?

753
00:33:35,040 --> 00:33:36,800
Things have come to this point,

754
00:33:37,440 --> 00:33:38,240
so I think

755
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:43,000
I have to tell you the truth.

756
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:57,480
Not a single one left.

757
00:33:57,800 --> 00:33:59,360
They registered them all under their name.

758
00:34:05,520 --> 00:34:08,560
Xuan Yan, I've wronged you.

759
00:34:10,239 --> 00:34:11,239
On this whole matter,

760
00:34:11,239 --> 00:34:13,280
I bear unshirkable responsibility.

761
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:16,000
I wanted to tell you many times,

762
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:16,800
but I...

763
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:18,560
I truly didn't know.

764
00:34:18,560 --> 00:34:19,560
Enough, Xin Ran.

765
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:25,080
I still remember when I was in that tiny room,

766
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:27,280
running online auctions,

767
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:30,679
you saw my potential and gave me a chance.

768
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:31,880
I remember it all.

769
00:34:32,199 --> 00:34:34,239
Later, that...

770
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:39,159
stuttering VP Zhang and the chairman

771
00:34:39,159 --> 00:34:41,400
distrusted me and gave me a hard time.

772
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:43,840
It was you who shouldered it for me, time and again.

773
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:46,000
You know what?

774
00:34:46,000 --> 00:34:48,080
From the very bottom of my heart,

775
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:49,960
I'm so incredibly grateful to you.

776
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:51,120
I know.

777
00:34:51,120 --> 00:34:53,960
But do you know how much I trusted you?

778
00:34:57,120 --> 00:34:59,400
Yes, I'm at fault here.

779
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,400
I betrayed the trust you placed in me.

780
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:04,000
But Xuan Yan, don't act on impulse.

781
00:35:04,600 --> 00:35:07,000
This can still be negotiated.

782
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:09,200
The co-op project can still move forward.

783
00:35:09,200 --> 00:35:10,400
As long as you're willing to back down,

784
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:12,960
go apologize to the chairman.

785
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:14,600
Leave the rest to me.

786
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:15,600
I'll convince him, okay?

787
00:35:15,600 --> 00:35:16,360
Xin Ran.

788
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:17,040
Xin Ran.

789
00:35:20,120 --> 00:35:21,480
I don't trust you anymore.

790
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:24,240
Xuan Yan!

791
00:35:25,240 --> 00:35:26,040
Xuan Yan!

792
00:35:26,600 --> 00:35:27,440
Xuan Yan!

793
00:35:41,160 --> 00:35:42,560
Zheng Guohui is truly ruthless.

794
00:35:43,160 --> 00:35:44,840
So many companies got involved,

795
00:35:44,840 --> 00:35:46,480
bought equipment, hired workers.

796
00:35:46,480 --> 00:35:48,400
The thing is, many of them

797
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:49,760
took out loans, borrowed money.

798
00:35:50,520 --> 00:35:51,800
Now telling everyone to stop?

799
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:53,320
That could drive people to their deaths!

800
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:55,640
And the roadshow this weekend, what do we do?

801
00:35:56,720 --> 00:35:58,280
It's not just the weekend roadshow.

802
00:35:58,440 --> 00:35:59,400
There are also many

803
00:36:00,040 --> 00:36:02,280
investors ready to fund offline stores.

804
00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:04,120
There's no way to explain this to them.

805
00:36:06,560 --> 00:36:07,400
Xuan Yan.

806
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:10,440
I don't think Sister Xin Ran meant to harm you.

807
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,560
She had no choice either.

808
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:15,480
The co-op proceeds as originally planned.

809
00:36:15,560 --> 00:36:17,680
The roadshow goes on as scheduled.

810
00:36:18,040 --> 00:36:20,080
Since Zheng Guohui has turned against me,

811
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:22,880
I'll fight him to the bitter end.

812
00:36:23,640 --> 00:36:25,120
I refuse to believe

813
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:27,560
that with such despicable tactics,

814
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:29,920
they can twist the truth.

815
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:31,880
What they did was

816
00:36:31,920 --> 00:36:33,360
maliciously register my patent first.

817
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:35,640
But they forgot, I'm the designer.

818
00:36:36,200 --> 00:36:38,280
I documented the entire development process.

819
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:41,560
Even if this lawsuit drags on forever,

820
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:43,720
I'll see it through to the end.

821
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:46,040
You want to grab the patent back?

822
00:36:46,120 --> 00:36:48,160
Not snatch. Take it back.

823
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:49,640
It's mine.

824
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:51,720
Have you thought about the worst-case scenario?

825
00:36:52,320 --> 00:36:54,040
Even if the sky falls,

826
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:56,160
I'll bear it.

827
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:07,480
Hello, Chairman.

828
00:37:08,080 --> 00:37:09,720
I've been calling but you didn't pick up.

829
00:37:09,720 --> 00:37:10,800
I figured you were busy.

830
00:37:11,040 --> 00:37:11,720
Here's the thing.

831
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:13,760
Our county's Commerce Bureau

832
00:37:14,080 --> 00:37:16,320
is organizing a trip to Shenzhen.

833
00:37:16,800 --> 00:37:18,200
That's your neck of the woods, right?

834
00:37:18,200 --> 00:37:19,440
I'd like to meet with you.

835
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:21,160
Yes, I'll be heading out tomorrow.

836
00:37:21,280 --> 00:37:22,280
How about this, Chairman.

837
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:24,040
I'll contact you when I arrive.

838
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:24,800
Alright.

839
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:26,400
I really want to pay you a visit.

840
00:37:27,040 --> 00:37:28,000
Whenever you're free.

841
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:29,360
Thank you, thank you.

842
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:32,960
Secretary Peng, what do you think?

843
00:37:33,880 --> 00:37:35,600
Don't get your hopes too high.

844
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:37,280
Zheng Guohui is no simple man.

845
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:39,520
He rarely listens to anyone else.

846
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:42,000
Especially when core interests are involved.

847
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:45,640
This is a huge hidden threat.

848
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:47,400
It could explode at any moment,

849
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:48,880
with unthinkable consequences.

850
00:37:50,520 --> 00:37:51,480
It's my fault.

851
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:53,040
I didn't think it through carefully enough.

852
00:37:53,480 --> 00:37:54,440
At the time, I only thought about

853
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:56,040
setting up the co-op quickly.

854
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:57,120
I really didn't expect

855
00:37:57,120 --> 00:37:58,520
such a huge landmine was buried in it.

856
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:03,280
It's okay. Recognizing the problem is progress.

857
00:38:03,360 --> 00:38:05,760
But now isn't the time to review.

858
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:07,280
We need to find a way to deal with it.

859
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:09,280
I've consulted a lawyer.

860
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:11,800
The lawyer said if we go through legal channels,

861
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:12,880
the outcome won't be optimistic.

862
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:15,080
Litigation takes a long time.

863
00:38:16,720 --> 00:38:18,160
Notify Xuan Yan immediately.

864
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:20,640
Have him halt all co-op activities.

865
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:22,000
Minimize the losses.

866
00:38:22,120 --> 00:38:24,960
The problem is Xuan Yan won't listen.

867
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:27,360
No matter what I say, he won't budge.

868
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:31,160
Xuan Yan is young and hot-headed.

869
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:33,680
He may not be able to accept this reality.

870
00:38:33,880 --> 00:38:34,960
If that's the case,

871
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:36,960
we need to prepare for the worst.

872
00:38:41,560 --> 00:38:43,440
Contact Chairman Xiao right away.

873
00:38:43,880 --> 00:38:45,040
I need to meet with him immediately.

874
00:38:45,040 --> 00:38:46,080
We need to find out

875
00:38:46,080 --> 00:38:47,160
about all the businesses in the co-op,

876
00:38:47,160 --> 00:38:48,640
their investment situation.

877
00:38:48,680 --> 00:38:50,000
Keep the losses to a minimum.

878
00:38:51,280 --> 00:38:53,560
Also, communicate with the people.

879
00:38:53,560 --> 00:38:54,920
Prevent the situation from escalating.

880
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:56,840
Yiran.

881
00:38:57,280 --> 00:39:00,080
Have a proper talk with Xuan Yan.

882
00:39:00,640 --> 00:39:03,560
Get him to reach an agreement with Zheng Guohui.

883
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:04,920
Businessmen chase profit.

884
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:07,480
Whether to cooperate or fight,

885
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:10,680
depends on which benefits them more.

886
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:13,200
Understood.

887
00:39:38,160 --> 00:39:38,960
Sister Xin,

888
00:39:39,080 --> 00:39:40,760
The production progress meeting is coming up.

889
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:42,840
Cancel it. We're not having it.

890
00:39:43,360 --> 00:39:44,760
Canceling out of nowhere?

891
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,640
I don't know if VP Zhang will again...

892
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:48,320
I said, cancel it.

893
00:39:49,240 --> 00:39:49,760
Okay.

894
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:08,280
Here, Chairman Xiao, please.

895
00:40:08,520 --> 00:40:09,760
Come, come, please.

896
00:40:11,320 --> 00:40:13,360
Shouldn't we give Daya Zhai a heads-up first?

897
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:14,520
Wouldn't that be inappropriate?

898
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:15,960
Secretary,

899
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:17,640
I think we need to tread carefully here.

900
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:20,080
If Daya Zhai beats us to it,

901
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,480
we'll be left on the back foot.

902
00:40:21,640 --> 00:40:22,440
Director Ge,

903
00:40:22,680 --> 00:40:25,240
I still think we shouldn't tell everyone yet.

904
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:26,640
Why not?

905
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:28,880
First, things haven't reached the worst-case scenario.

906
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:30,320
Second,

907
00:40:30,680 --> 00:40:31,920
if we tell everyone,

908
00:40:32,120 --> 00:40:33,520
they'll panic at the slightest rumor.

909
00:40:33,680 --> 00:40:36,320
Then the mess would be even harder to clean up.

910
00:40:37,400 --> 00:40:38,160
Let's hold off.

911
00:40:38,560 --> 00:40:39,560
Don't say anything for now.

912
00:40:40,240 --> 00:40:41,520
But if problems come up later

913
00:40:41,520 --> 00:40:42,800
and can't be dealt with in time, what then?

914
00:40:43,200 --> 00:40:45,040
They'll come running to us, won't they?

915
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:50,880
Director Ge, I understand your concerns.

916
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:52,960
How about this?

917
00:40:53,160 --> 00:40:54,360
I'll just send out a notice,

918
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:55,160
saying that

919
00:40:56,600 --> 00:40:58,960
we're adjusting our design direction.

920
00:40:59,160 --> 00:41:01,320
Then have each factory pause for now.

921
00:41:01,640 --> 00:41:03,720
Once we have a new design plan,

922
00:41:04,040 --> 00:41:05,160
we'll resume.

923
00:41:05,280 --> 00:41:06,320
Would that work?

924
00:41:06,520 --> 00:41:06,960
Alright.

925
00:41:07,600 --> 00:41:10,000
Let's go with Chairman Xiao's approach then,

926
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:10,960
and see how it plays out.

927
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:13,440
And keep a close eye on how things develop.

928
00:41:14,160 --> 00:41:14,760
Okay.

929
00:41:14,760 --> 00:41:16,160
Then let's go with this plan.

930
00:41:16,160 --> 00:41:16,600
Please, sit.

931
00:41:16,600 --> 00:41:17,160
No, no, no.

932
00:41:17,160 --> 00:41:19,200
I need to take a call, alright?

933
00:41:19,200 --> 00:41:20,320
We'll discuss anything else later, okay?

934
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:20,600
Okay, okay, okay.

935
00:41:20,600 --> 00:41:21,520
Sorry, gotta take this call.

936
00:42:42,600 --> 00:42:44,160
You... just leave me alone.

937
00:42:44,160 --> 00:42:45,200
Don't you worry.

938
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:49,040
If you're drunk, I can't handle you.

939
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:52,840
What did you want from me?

940
00:42:55,760 --> 00:42:58,320
Xiao Min, go talk some sense into Xuan Yan, okay?
